hama pedoM se girawe hue pawwoM ko waWA bAzXa se bahawe hue pAnI ko xeKawe hEM .
samaya ke sAWa sWiwi kEse parivarwiwa howI hE ?
visWApana meM parimANa va xiSA xonoM howe hEM.
Osawa vega kA qNAwmaka yA XanAwmaka honA visWApana ke cihna para nirBara karawA hE .
sAmAnyawaH vaswu kI gawi kI avaXi meM usake vega meM parivarwana howA rahawA hE .
yaha samasyA gElIliyo ke samaya BI WI .
isa guNanaPala ko Avega kahawe hEM.
vaswu ke isa guNa ko jadawva kahawe hEM.
yaha pATyAMka @T 1 pariveSa kA wApa hE.
isa saMbaMXa ko AxarSa gEsa niyama kahawe hEM.
yaha sarala Avarwa gawi xarSAwA hE.
yaha @rms mAnoM kI avaXAraNA ke lABa xarSAwI hE.
isase xviXruva AGUrNa kI pariBARA kA safkewa milawA hE.
yaha saxiSa guNana hE.
yaha prakriyA wAwkRaNika howI hE.
isa prakriyA ko moYdulana kahawe hEM.
aXika yaWArWawA se , @a nikAya ke saMhawi kenxra kA wvaraNa hE .
hara BujA kI lambAI eka axiSa hE waWA parimApa BI eka axiSa hE .
saFcAra sUcanA ke sampreRaNa kI kriyA hE.
olIka amla aNu ke sAija kA Akalana karane kI eka sarala viXi nIce xI gaI hE.
